Use this endpoint to retrieve all Profile Fields for an Event.

### HTTP Request

`GET https://invitepeople.com/api/v2/events/<EVENT_ID>/profile_fields`

### URL Parameters

Parameter | Description
--------- | -----------
**EVENT_ID**&nbsp;`required` | The ID of the Event.

