```

Use this endpoint to retrieve a specific Profile Field.

### HTTP Request

`GET https://invitepeople.com/api/v2/profile_fields/<ID>`

### URL Parameters

Parameter | Description
--------- | -----------
**ID**&nbsp;`required` | The ID of the Profile Field.
